T er konjunkturutsatte bransjer.", "- Dotcom-boblen rundt \u00e5r 2000 viser at tidene svinger ogs\u00e5 for IT. Jeg er ikke enig i at olje er mer konjunkturutsatt enn andre bransjer, sier Egil Tj\u00e5land."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|okonomi"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "c980f3feb77cc4bbf2adb74a2f9c16ff72119b7094e78f7cb230be96a195a30a"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-29T04:14:02.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "- At f\u00e6rre \u00f8nsker \u00e5 studere oljefag er et sunnhetstegn for norsk \u00f8konomi, mener Thor Richard Isaksen i teknologibedriften Zedge."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/okonomi/article14737184.ece/a0xxes/ALTERNATES/w980-default/zedge5%20(2).jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/5f132789314db47b12e0e05d328c0ebc848254cd.jpg?597d0e52"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Et sunnhetstegn at studenter dropper olje -adressa.no", "- Uansvarlig l\u00f8fte", "- Lettere \u00e5 omstille", "- Gapet \u00f8ker", "Helt uenig"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "5f132789314db47b12e0e05d328c0ebc848254cd"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Nyskaping", "omstilling", "zedge", "oljebransjen"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Nyskaping,omstilling,zedge,oljebransjen"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "okonomi"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["norsk \u00f8konomi", "bransje", "olje", "studenter dropper olje", "studenter"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["zedge", "oljedirektoratet", "institutt", "t. jeg"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["europa", "trondheim", "russland", "norge", "new york"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["thor richar